# Drug Discovery Workflow: Malaria Target Analysis using ChEMBL

## Overview
This notebook performs a complete drug discovery workflow:
1. Target Identification (Plasmodium falciparum protein)
2. Bioactivity Data Retrieval from ChEMBL
3. Molecular Descriptor Calculation with RDKit
4. Data Analysis and Lead Compound Identification

